00:41:00,875 --> 00:41:03,586
Tidak ada alasan untukku merasa takut.

667
00:41:04,796 --> 00:41:06,130
James sudah ketemu.

668
00:41:07,256 --> 00:41:11,010
Untunglah kau meneleponku, Prof. Kim.
