00:47:54,914 --> 00:47:57,541
Kalian gagal?

801
00:48:02,880 --> 00:48:04,590
Bagaimana sidangnya?

802
00:48:04,673 --> 00:48:06,842
Dia seharusnya ditahan di balai sidang,

803
00:48:06,926 --> 00:48:08,427
tapi dia akan segera dipenjara.

