00:52:44,953 --> 00:52:46,830
- Hentikan.
- Panggil aku "Kak."

879
00:52:47,498 --> 00:52:48,499
Kak.

880
00:52:50,167 --> 00:52:53,253
Kalian sedang apa di sini?
Kukira sedang bersedih.

881
00:52:53,921 --> 00:52:55,255
Aku sedih karena kita kalah.

